1
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:35,000
[Wind Direction]

2
00:01:35,479 --> 00:01:37,940
[Episode 7]

3
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,410
[Winter, 1987]

4
00:01:39,990 --> 00:01:40,920
It's all yours.

5
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,320
Don't be mad at me anymore.

6
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:42,990
If they

7
00:01:43,030 --> 00:01:44,070
bully you two again in the future,

8
00:01:44,070 --> 00:01:46,670
I'll knock all three of them out with one punch.

9
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:47,380
No.

10
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:48,430
I will.

11
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:51,680
There isn't a "Skillful Star, Wanderer Yan Qing" card.

12
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,120
Why do you want his cards?

13
00:01:53,430 --> 00:01:55,979
I only have one "Wanderer Yan Qing" card.

14
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:58,390
Then you can become best friends

15
00:01:58,390 --> 00:01:59,350
with Yan Qing.

16
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:00,770
Hu, come on, let's take a picture.

17
00:02:00,190 --> 00:02:04,120
[Linqi Oilfield]

18
00:02:02,450 --> 00:02:04,180
I'll give the card to you, okay?

19
00:02:09,610 --> 00:02:10,669
If anyone

20
00:02:10,669 --> 00:02:11,730
bullies Hu and me again,

21
00:02:11,730 --> 00:02:12,910
and you don't step in,

22
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:14,790
even a thousand hero cards won't make up for it.

23
00:02:14,790 --> 00:02:16,160
Okay, pinky swear.

24
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:16,860
From now on, the three of us

25
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:18,460
will be an inseparable trio.

26
00:02:20,930 --> 00:02:26,770
Pinky swear; no breaking it for a hundred years.

27
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,440
Let's seal it with a stamp.

28
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:29,880
Come on, Min.

29
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:30,890
You three, stand in a line.

30
00:02:30,890 --> 00:02:32,690
I'm going to take a photo for you.

31
00:02:33,510 --> 00:02:34,630
Come on, look at me.

32
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,990
Come on. Three, two, one. Smile.

33
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,880
[Inseparable Trio]

34
00:02:43,380 --> 00:02:44,780
Stand there. Don't move!

35
00:02:44,990 --> 00:02:45,880
Don't move!

36
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,710
Don't move!

37
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:49,960
Don't move!

38
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,240
Don't move!

39
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,070
Listen!

40
00:02:53,070 --> 00:02:54,200
We've been watching you for days.

41
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,930
Gathering people for gambling in broad daylight!

42
00:02:55,930 --> 00:02:56,880
You've got some nerve!

43
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,880
What do you do?

44
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,620
Shut up! This is an operation!

45
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:01,370
Officer,

46
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,990
this guy is the prime culprit!

47
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:03,950
Cuff him.

48
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:06,750
We work in the same unit.

49
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:07,580
-This way!
-Squat down!

50
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:08,390
You squat too.

51
00:03:08,550 --> 00:03:10,410
-I have to squat too?
-Squat down!

52
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:15,830
Cuff them all!

53
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,450
What happened?

54
00:03:39,670 --> 00:03:40,530
You're not hurt, are you?

55
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:41,410
We're fine.

56
00:03:41,829 --> 00:03:42,800
The three of us

57
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,750
just caught a man selling fake medicine,

58
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,070
so we brought him in.

59
00:03:45,070 --> 00:03:46,370
All statements have been recorded.

60
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:47,470
I'm innocent!

61
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,070
Innocent, my foot!

62
00:03:48,070 --> 00:03:49,620
Would you be cuffed if you were innocent?

63
00:03:49,620 --> 00:03:50,700
Alright. Alright.

64
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,760
Why... is Baoshan here too?

65
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,300
Ask him yourself.

66
00:03:54,650 --> 00:03:55,190
What happened?

67
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:56,030
He was gambling at the farmers' market

68
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:56,920
and was caught in the act.

69
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,990
I wasn't gambling.

70
00:03:58,020 --> 00:03:59,100
Say that again!

71
00:03:59,120 --> 00:03:59,990
You squat down!

72
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,190
After I knew someone had reported it,

73
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:04,590
I went there to catch the bad guys, Pengfei.

74
00:04:04,810 --> 00:04:05,940
Why are you two here?

75
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:08,700
I'm truly being wronged.

76
00:04:08,730 --> 00:04:09,730
I didn't do anything.

77
00:04:09,730 --> 00:04:10,590
I was at the door when he came to me,

78
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,530
and we got into a scuffle.

79
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:13,310
I was brought here  when I was dragged into that room.

80
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:13,790
Why did you two

81
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:14,750
fight?

82
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:16,670
Why did you come and fight me?

83
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:17,930
He wanted to go inside,

84
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,070
but I wouldn't let him!

85
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,250
You watch your mouth!

86
00:04:20,250 --> 00:04:21,029
Who wanted to go in?

87
00:04:21,029 --> 00:04:22,590
I was there to send money to my uncle.

88
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:23,470
You watch your mouth!

89
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:24,280
I was there to catch bad guys.

90
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:25,270
Why did I need money?

91
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:27,530
Why are you chatting? Shut up, all of you!

92
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:31,030
It's truly a shame.

93
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:33,030
I was out catching a bad guy,

94
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:34,900
while my son has become a gambler.

95
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:36,300
What kind of life is this?

96
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,909
Your son, Yaya, is so good.

97
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:41,250
He is sensible and never causes trouble.

98
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:42,330
They're both boys,

99
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,030
but why did I end up with one like this?

100
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,630
I wasn't gambling!

101
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,630
Officer,

102
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:50,870
why don't you just arrest him

103
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,030
and lock him up?

104
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:52,710
I'll leave you to deal with him.

105
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:53,870
I really can't discipline him anymore.

106
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,030
-Arrest him.
-Mom, what are you talking about?

107
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:56,430
-Yaya!
-Shut up.

108
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,310
Calm down.

109
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:59,170
We don't know the whole story yet.

110
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:03,750
Cheng Miaomiao, don't be mad at me.

111
00:05:04,770 --> 00:05:06,730
I'm really a victim this time.

112
00:05:05,150 --> 00:05:07,830
[Wancheng Road Police Station]

113
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,710
Really.

114
00:05:07,890 --> 00:05:09,360
First, I got robbed, and then I got falsely arrested.

115
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,710
The one who got me into this mess is Qiang Xiaowa!

116
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:12,230
Qiang Xiaowa was trying to save you.

117
00:05:12,230 --> 00:05:13,920
I don't need him to save me.

118
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:14,830
He saved...

119
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:22,500
Many people in our village

120
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,690
lost everything

121
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:25,320
in that gambling den.

122
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:27,610
That bridge...

123
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,150
The road on your side by the oilfield

124
00:05:29,150 --> 00:05:30,480
you have asphalt roads,

125
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:33,680
while on our side, it's nothing but muddy slush.

126
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:36,920
Have your shoes ever stepped in the mud?

127
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:45,040
What does stepping in the mud... have to do with this?

128
00:05:45,850 --> 00:05:46,560
Is your brain

129
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,110
full of mud?

130
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:48,909
You really don't understand

131
00:05:48,909 --> 00:05:49,950
what he meant?

132
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:51,710
What does he mean?

133
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,880
Slow down, slow down!

134
00:05:58,420 --> 00:05:58,990
Alright.

135
00:05:59,010 --> 00:05:59,930
Go lost now!

136
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,020
What are you doing?

137
00:06:01,050 --> 00:06:02,630
All right, you run!

138
00:06:06,460 --> 00:06:07,100
Right?

139
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:14,290
Yu, you've been kicking me the entire way here.

140
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:15,880
Listen, I really didn't do

141
00:06:15,910 --> 00:06:16,860
anything wrong this time!

142
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:17,990
Do you know that I...

143
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:19,870
Listen up!

144
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,690
Don't ever come to my house again!

145
00:06:22,690 --> 00:06:23,840
You don't do something good, and that's fine,

146
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,020
but you even dragged Li Si into this!

147
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:25,990
He is still a student,

148
00:06:25,990 --> 00:06:26,910
and you took him to gamble!

149
00:06:26,910 --> 00:06:28,590
Are you out of your mind?

150
00:06:30,070 --> 00:06:32,630
Yu, I really didn't take him to gamble.

151
00:06:32,650 --> 00:06:33,470
And I didn't even know

152
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:34,310
he went in later.

153
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,770
Besides, I didn't gamble!

154
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:36,740
See?

155
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:39,430
The money is all here.

156
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:40,120
Go back,

157
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,540
and don't come here again!

158
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:42,310
Yu, Yu.

159
00:06:42,330 --> 00:06:43,530
Calm down. Calm down.

160
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:45,500
How can I calm myself down?

161
00:06:45,670 --> 00:06:46,980
We just got fined 500 yuan!

162
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:48,000
500 yuan!

163
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:49,180
I'll pay you back.

164
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:50,320
When will you pay me back?

165
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,340
Give me a date.

166
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,630
At the end of the year.

167
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,000
It's only summer now.

168
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,840
Then, these months...

169
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:56,840
N-N-Next month.

170
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,110
I'll definitely pay you back next month, okay?

171
00:06:58,110 --> 00:06:59,150
Jia Baoshan, listen.

172
00:06:59,150 --> 00:06:59,909
If you ever come to my house again,

173
00:06:59,909 --> 00:07:01,110
I'll break your legs!

174
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,150
Alright. Alright.

175
00:07:02,150 --> 00:07:02,990
We're family.

176
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:04,470
Don't say that.

177
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:06,430
Baoshan, let me tell you.

178
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,350
Learn from your mistakes, alright?

179
00:07:08,350 --> 00:07:10,090
You have to correct your mistakes!

180
00:07:10,090 --> 00:07:11,060
From now on,

181
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:11,920
no more gambling.

182
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,670
There can't be a next time, understand?

183
00:07:13,670 --> 00:07:14,430
I got it.

184
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,080
Look at how good an attitude he's showing,

185
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:17,810
right?

186
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:18,950
Well...

187
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,850
calm down. Calm down.

188
00:07:20,890 --> 00:07:22,120
S-S-Stop staring at him.

189
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,140
Stop staring at him.

190
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:24,620
What about our hair?

191
00:07:26,530 --> 00:07:27,430
Move aside.

192
00:07:29,230 --> 00:07:31,240
How am I supposed to go to work like this tomorrow?

193
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:33,100
Well... how about we wear a hat tomorrow?

194
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,980
Wear a hat? No way!

195
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,430
How about I remove these and wash your hair?

196
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:37,260
Let's wash it now.

197
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,030
Starting tomorrow,

198
00:07:38,030 --> 00:07:40,090
you're not getting any pocket money!

199
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,540
And tonight, don't go to bed!

200
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:43,400
I'll just sit right here with you!

201
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:46,460
I think you have way too much energy!

202
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,680
Isn't that a bit much, Mom?

203
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,880
A bit much?

204
00:07:49,530 --> 00:07:50,140
Do you want me

205
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:51,030
to call your dad now

206
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:51,630
and ask him to come back?

207
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:52,960
No, no, no need. Well...

208
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,180
I don't want any pocket money anymore.

209
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:55,260
I don't want any pocket money anymore.

210
00:07:55,260 --> 00:07:56,520
You really piss me off!

211
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,450
Squat properly!

212
00:08:03,810 --> 00:08:05,290
You young people

213
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:06,770
need to resist temptation

214
00:08:07,410 --> 00:08:08,870
and stay on the right path.

215
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,160
Don't go astray.

216
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:12,340
So many people

217
00:08:12,370 --> 00:08:14,790
take one wrong step, leading to lifelong regret.

218
00:08:14,790 --> 00:08:16,040
This is all a lesson.

219
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,210
Uncle,

220
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,960
you should write that down

221
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,620
and read it from time to time when you're free.

222
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:23,190
Out of everyone in the family, you're the most reckless and dangerous.

223
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,300
I'm an adult.

224
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,450
I've seen the world.

225
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:26,700
When someone who's been through everything tells you something,

226
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:29,160
you have to listen with your heart, you know?

227
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:30,200
I...

228
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:32,750
Look at the time!

229
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:33,950
Hurry up, you two!

230
00:08:33,970 --> 00:08:35,750
Yeah, stop dawdling.

231
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,919
Listen to your teachers at school, alright?

232
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:39,480
Yu.

233
00:08:41,179 --> 00:08:42,240
I'm leaving, then.

234
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:44,210
When will you come back?

235
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:46,570
I'll be back once your mom cools down.

236
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:51,720
Stay for breakfast before you leave.

237
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,550
I'm too ashamed to eat.

238
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:53,550
See you, Pengfei.

239
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,040
Wait, take one of these too.

240
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,120
See you, my foot!

241
00:08:58,450 --> 00:08:59,760
So heartless!

242
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:02,760
Let's eat.

243
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,480
I patted my chest

244
00:09:07,510 --> 00:09:08,990
and promised Mr. Gao

245
00:09:09,010 --> 00:09:10,280
that I could definitely help Qiang Xiaowa

246
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,100
fit in with the group.

247
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,070
But things

248
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:13,220
haven't gone well at all.

249
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,590
Not only did I fail to bring him in,

250
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:16,030
but he also had a fight with you.

251
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:17,080
Now, you both

252
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:18,490
ended up at the police station last night.

253
00:09:18,490 --> 00:09:20,040
I thought that going through a tough time together

254
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,190
might bring us closer,

255
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:22,860
but it turned out that nothing changed. He's still the same.

256
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:24,100
Then forget it.

257
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,940
We don't have the necessary skills,

258
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,540
and he's not a delicate task.

259
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:29,460
Qiang Xiaowa has saved you twice

260
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,060
in critical moments,

261
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,720
Li Si.

262
00:09:32,110 --> 00:09:33,510
You owe him so much.

263
00:09:34,450 --> 00:09:36,540
Yesterday, the cops scolded me,

264
00:09:36,540 --> 00:09:37,460
my mom scolded me,

265
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:38,740
and I spent the entire night half-squatting with a basin on my head.

266
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:39,580
What more do you want from me?

267
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:41,510
One should always repay kindness!

268
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:43,090
But it seems like he doesn't really need us

269
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:44,570
to return his kindness.

270
00:09:44,820 --> 00:09:46,650
He has been here for many days,

271
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:48,700
yet he hasn't said a word to you or even looked at you,

272
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,360
and he always looks so fierce.

273
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,410
Fierce?

274
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:56,020
I really don't feel that way.

275
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:58,340
I think he just feels self-conscious

276
00:09:58,340 --> 00:09:59,580
because he doesn't speak Mandarin well.

277
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,940
I'm running for Class Monitor next week.

278
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:01,570
If I

279
00:10:01,570 --> 00:10:02,630
don't handle this well,

280
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:04,630
it will definitely affect my votes.

281
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,390
I've got to try everything.

282
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:07,470
I refuse to lose!

