00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,720
You have a first love?

566
00:21:04,370 --> 00:21:05,720
I don't even know that.

567
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,010
How could you not know?

568
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:09,750
Who is it?

569
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:12,660
Guess.

570
00:21:14,810 --> 00:21:15,590
Li Si,

571
00:21:15,620 --> 00:21:17,330
are you worse than an animal?

572
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:19,160
We're together all the time,

573
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,220
yet you still keep secrets from me?

574
00:21:20,220 --> 00:21:20,980
-No.
-You said

575
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:21,860
that you'd marry me when you were three.

576
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:22,700
Even though I didn't agree,

577
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:23,820
you changed your mind so quickly.

578
00:21:23,820 --> 00:21:24,810
Let go of me!

579
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:27,090
When have I changed my mind?

580
00:21:27,450 --> 00:21:28,490
I'm a real man!

581
00:21:28,910 --> 00:21:29,750
I'm not my dad.

582
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:43,850
What's wrong with your dad?

583
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:57,870
Fate is cruel.

584
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:25,700
Fate is cruel.

585
00:22:26,570 --> 00:22:27,290
Dad!

586
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:29,720
Fate is cruel.

587
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:32,530
You've been drinking again, haven't you?

588
00:22:32,530 --> 00:22:33,460
Who is speaking?

589
00:22:34,940 --> 00:22:35,620
Who?

590
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:37,230
Me, your son.

591
00:22:37,250 --> 00:22:38,050
My son?

592
00:22:40,230 --> 00:22:41,570
My son is good, my son.

593
00:22:44,170 --> 00:22:45,410
My son is handsome.

594
00:22:48,870 --> 00:22:51,110
My son has sparkling eyes.

595
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:54,350
My son needs to study diligently.

596
00:22:54,490 --> 00:22:56,000
You can't drink.

597
00:22:56,780 --> 00:22:57,730
Drinking...

598
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:00,100
will make you stupid.

599
00:23:00,110 --> 00:23:00,790
Yes.

600
00:23:01,270 --> 00:23:02,750
You are a living example.

601
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:05,100
Seeing you like this, I won't drink either.

602
00:23:05,100 --> 00:23:05,730
Let's go home.

603
00:23:05,730 --> 00:23:07,060
No... I didn't drink.

604
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,100
I did.

605
00:23:08,820 --> 00:23:09,340
Get up.

606
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:11,740
Get... up.

607
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:13,640
Why are the stairs slippery?

608
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:15,060
They're so slippery.

609
00:23:16,260 --> 00:23:17,100
Let's go home.

610
00:23:17,130 --> 00:23:18,190
I'll open the door.

611
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:19,940
There is no keyhole.

612
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:21,350
Which one is the keyhole?

613
00:23:21,370 --> 00:23:23,400
Insert it upwards if you can't see the keyhole.

614
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:24,580
The door is already open for you.

615
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:25,660
Let's go. Come up.

616
00:23:25,660 --> 00:23:26,730
That's not the keyhole.

617
00:23:26,730 --> 00:23:27,770
It's up there.

618
00:23:31,570 --> 00:23:33,030
-Let's go.
-It's up there.

619
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:34,870
No, my photo.

620
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:35,920
Let me get it for you.

621
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:36,580
My photo.

622
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:46,060
Don't let your mom see it.

623
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:51,070
Is that your dad in the photo?

624
00:23:51,100 --> 00:23:52,550
I know it's him with just one glance.

625
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:54,340
He looks thinner than he does now.

626
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:55,290
but my dad was quite handsome

627
00:23:55,290 --> 00:23:56,290
when he was young.

628
00:23:56,860 --> 00:23:58,140
That girl must be my dad's first love.

629
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:58,930
Her name is Bai Shuang.

630
00:23:58,930 --> 00:24:00,060
I still remember it.

631
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:03,100
Then, does your mom know about this?

632
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:05,670
How can I tell this to her? Am I stupid?

633
00:24:09,330 --> 00:24:11,660
Crying while holding Bai Shuang's photo,

634
00:24:12,250 --> 00:24:13,530
what does that mean?

635
00:24:16,620 --> 00:24:17,730
He must have done something

636
00:24:17,730 --> 00:24:19,340
that hurt Bai Shuang.

637
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:21,090
So, I suspect

638
00:24:23,210 --> 00:24:25,090
that my dad abandoned his first love, Bai Shuang,

639
00:24:25,090 --> 00:24:26,210
and married my mom

640
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:28,410
solely because my grandpa is a leader.

641
00:24:28,410 --> 00:24:30,540
I guess my dad doesn't even love my mom.

642
00:24:31,810 --> 00:24:33,470
God works in mysterious ways.

643
00:24:34,130 --> 00:24:35,890
Then, your dad is Linghu Chong.

644
00:24:35,890 --> 00:24:37,690
No, he is Chen Shimei!

645
00:24:44,740 --> 00:24:46,930
Has Luo Zheng been bullying you lately?

646
00:24:46,930 --> 00:24:48,210
Why would he bully me?

647
00:24:49,040 --> 00:24:50,570
I heard from Wei Xue

648
00:24:50,570 --> 00:24:52,340
that Luo Zheng always bullies Yuan Shanqing.

649
00:24:52,340 --> 00:24:53,890
If he were in our class,

650
00:24:53,890 --> 00:24:56,020
I'd teach him a lesson sooner or later.

651
00:24:56,050 --> 00:24:57,380
If he really bullies you,

652
00:24:57,380 --> 00:24:58,890
come upstairs to find me. You hear me?

653
00:24:58,890 --> 00:25:00,010
I don't need you to.

654
00:25:00,990 --> 00:25:02,180
I'll help you.

655
00:25:02,210 --> 00:25:03,900
I support you in helping Yuan Shanqing.

656
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:04,810
She's pitiful enough.

657
00:25:04,810 --> 00:25:06,690
How could he push her to the edge?

658
00:25:09,130 --> 00:25:10,790
What does it have to do with you two?

659
00:25:10,790 --> 00:25:12,130
No need for you two to stick out.

660
00:25:12,130 --> 00:25:13,250
If you have time for this,

661
00:25:13,250 --> 00:25:14,490
how about focusing on studying?

662
00:25:14,490 --> 00:25:16,130
What are you trying to show off?

663
00:25:16,130 --> 00:25:16,700
Mom.

664
00:25:17,050 --> 00:25:18,380
Lawrence said,

665
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:19,890
"A youth should make righteousness

666
00:25:19,890 --> 00:25:22,020
the foundation of all their actions."

667
00:25:22,620 --> 00:25:23,930
You... you learned that from your dad, didn't you?

668
00:25:23,930 --> 00:25:25,210
All this nitpicking and quoting.

669
00:25:25,210 --> 00:25:27,290
What's the darn use of spouting grand principles?

670
00:25:27,290 --> 00:25:28,410
And Lawrence.

671
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,900
Who's this Lawrence?

672
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:33,170
Mom, Lawrence is...

673
00:25:34,410 --> 00:25:35,620
a foreign people.

674
00:25:36,570 --> 00:25:37,750
Good for you, Miaomiao.

675
00:25:37,750 --> 00:25:39,280
Your English has improved.

676
00:25:39,290 --> 00:25:40,570
You're brave enough to speak English now.

677
00:25:40,570 --> 00:25:42,370
Yes, Father.

678
00:25:43,300 --> 00:25:45,370
[Linqi Oilfield No. 2 High School]

679
00:26:05,330 --> 00:26:06,860
We are good friends, right?

680
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:09,930
For the sake of our friendship,

681
00:26:09,930 --> 00:26:11,770
vote for me later when we elect the Class Monitor.

682
00:26:11,770 --> 00:26:13,020
This way, I can look out for you better,

683
00:26:13,020 --> 00:26:13,690
you know?

684
00:26:15,780 --> 00:26:16,690
Did you hear me?

685
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:20,730
Okay, it's a deal, then.

686
00:26:41,210 --> 00:26:42,670
-Class begins.
-Stand up.

687
00:26:43,770 --> 00:26:46,710
Good morning, Mr. Gao.

688
00:26:46,730 --> 00:26:48,260
Hello, everyone. Sit down.

689
00:26:50,410 --> 00:26:51,100
Today,

690
00:26:52,370 --> 00:26:54,190
we're going to select class leaders.

691
00:26:54,190 --> 00:26:55,300
You can vote.

692
00:26:55,330 --> 00:26:56,870
[Class 1, Grade 1]

693
00:26:57,930 --> 00:26:59,500
Cheng Yaya, 33 votes,

694
00:26:59,530 --> 00:27:01,390
was elected as the Study Monitor.

695
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:07,770
Next,

696
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,340
we'll be electing the Sports Monitor.

697
00:27:09,340 --> 00:27:10,340
Does anyone

698
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:11,870
have any other candidates?

699
00:27:13,890 --> 00:27:14,690
Cheng Yaya.

700
00:27:16,860 --> 00:27:18,450
For the position of Sports Monitor,

701
00:27:18,450 --> 00:27:19,710
I recommend Luo Zheng.

702
00:27:20,810 --> 00:27:21,410
Luo Zheng?

703
00:27:21,730 --> 00:27:22,650
Why him?

704
00:27:23,380 --> 00:27:24,810
Luo Zheng's sports performance

705
00:27:24,810 --> 00:27:26,340
has always been excellent.

706
00:27:26,490 --> 00:27:28,890
He also has a strong sense of right and wrong

707
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:29,910
and is skilled

708
00:27:29,930 --> 00:27:30,990
in various sports.

709
00:27:32,170 --> 00:27:33,610
Our class leaders' election

710
00:27:33,610 --> 00:27:34,370
doesn't necessarily have to be

711
00:27:34,370 --> 00:27:36,170
based on academic performance.

712
00:27:37,010 --> 00:27:38,250
Different class leaders

713
00:27:38,250 --> 00:27:39,850
will serve different roles.

714
00:27:40,530 --> 00:27:42,340
We should each play to our strengths.

715
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:43,180
If Luo Zheng

716
00:27:43,180 --> 00:27:44,530
is elected as Sports Monitor,

717
00:27:44,530 --> 00:27:45,330
I believe

718
00:27:45,530 --> 00:27:46,250
he can lead

719
00:27:46,250 --> 00:27:47,140
our whole class

720
00:27:47,140 --> 00:27:49,070
to enhance our sports performance

721
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:50,500
and achieve a good ranking

722
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:51,540
in sports meets.

723
00:27:52,970 --> 00:27:55,290
That's what makes an excellent Sports Monitor.

724
00:27:55,290 --> 00:27:55,860
Okay,

725
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:57,780
those who agree with Luo Zheng

726
00:27:57,780 --> 00:28:00,640
being the Sports Monitor, please raise your hands.

727
00:28:09,090 --> 00:28:10,530
Then I'll announce the votes directly.

728
00:28:10,530 --> 00:28:13,130
The one with the highest votes will be elected.

729
00:28:16,050 --> 00:28:16,820
Zhu Chao.

730
00:28:24,010 --> 00:28:24,690
Zhu Chao!

731
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:30,960
[Class Monitor]

732
00:28:30,490 --> 00:28:31,460
Xu Wenwu.

733
00:28:39,330 --> 00:28:40,260
Cheng Miaomiao.

734
00:28:45,650 --> 00:28:46,380
Zhu Chao.

735
00:28:56,370 --> 00:28:57,970
Cheng is the bigger one here.

736
00:28:58,730 --> 00:28:59,860
Turned the enemy into a friend

737
00:28:59,860 --> 00:29:01,050
and won him over.

738
00:29:02,290 --> 00:29:03,420
If Yuan Shanqing

739
00:29:03,420 --> 00:29:04,330
were as ugly as sin,

740
00:29:04,330 --> 00:29:05,860
would Cheng still help her?

741
00:29:09,770 --> 00:29:10,780
Why not?

742
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:12,020
Yes.

743
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:16,540
Students of Class 1 of Grade 1, assemble!

744
00:29:16,540 --> 00:29:18,610
See? The new official has taken office.

745
00:29:18,610 --> 00:29:20,470
We have to run 1,500 meters today.

746
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:22,500
What are you three doing?

747
00:29:23,190 --> 00:29:23,890
Let's run.

748
00:29:23,890 --> 00:29:25,530
Coming. Coming.

749
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:33,310
[Zhu Chao, Xu Wenwu, Cheng Miaomiao]

750
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:33,310
[Class Monitor]

751
00:29:32,490 --> 00:29:33,460
Miaomiao.

752
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,070
Don't...

753
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:35,450
Let me explain, okay?

754
00:29:36,250 --> 00:29:36,770
Miaomiao!

755
00:29:36,770 --> 00:29:38,540
Why aren't you even attending PE class anymore?

756
00:29:38,540 --> 00:29:40,620
I don't even want to go to school anymore.

757
00:29:40,620 --> 00:29:42,100
Miaomiao, let me explain.

758
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:44,380
Forget it.

759
00:29:45,660 --> 00:29:46,790
It's all in the past.

760
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:50,080
The past is like a vanishing mist.

761
00:29:52,060 --> 00:29:53,450
It's not that I didn't choose you...

762
00:29:53,450 --> 00:29:55,300
Well, even if I had chosen you,

763
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:57,180
you'd only have two votes.

764
00:29:57,250 --> 00:29:58,060
It's still useless.

765
00:29:58,060 --> 00:29:59,540
Even so, you shouldn't have voted for Zhu Chao either.

766
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:00,610
I didn't vote for Zhu Chao.

767
00:30:00,610 --> 00:30:01,740
I voted for Xu Wenwu.

768
00:30:05,770 --> 00:30:07,130
Miaomiao, it's okay.

769
00:30:07,650 --> 00:30:09,180
We don't need to be the Class Monitor.

770
00:30:09,180 --> 00:30:10,090
Big deal.

771
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,120
Don't be upset.

772
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:12,680
I'm upset now,

773
00:30:12,700 --> 00:30:14,620
not because I wasn't elected as the Class Monitor,

774
00:30:14,620 --> 00:30:16,480
but because... I can't figure out

775
00:30:17,390 --> 00:30:19,840
why even Xu Wenwu got higher votes than me.

776
00:30:20,250 --> 00:30:22,050
His study is not that much better than mine.

777
00:30:22,050 --> 00:30:23,060
Has he ever done anything

778
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:24,510
for this class?

779
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:26,830
Has he ever placed in any sports meets?

780
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,480
Have we not placed either?

781
00:30:29,690 --> 00:30:31,370
In the tug-of-war last semester,

782
00:30:31,370 --> 00:30:32,330
didn't I play

783
00:30:32,350 --> 00:30:33,450
a decisive role?

784
00:30:33,450 --> 00:30:34,490
Without my strategy,

785
00:30:34,490 --> 00:30:35,530
could our class have won?

786
00:30:35,530 --> 00:30:37,660
Our class relies on me for many things!

787
00:30:38,130 --> 00:30:39,620
Which one relies on you?

788
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:41,610
There are too many. I...

789
00:30:41,890 --> 00:30:43,620
I don't even want to list them all.

790
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:44,530
Let's not talk about the past.

791
00:30:44,530 --> 00:30:46,140
Let's talk about the new student, Qiang Xiaowa.

792
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:47,330
Which of them

793
00:30:47,330 --> 00:30:48,210
has genuinely wanted to help him?

794
00:30:48,210 --> 00:30:49,170
Wasn't it I

795
00:30:49,170 --> 00:30:50,210
who took on this important task?

796
00:30:50,210 --> 00:30:51,820
Aren't you helping him

797
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:52,500
just because you wanted to become the Class Monitor?

798
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:55,220
Wrong! I'm just grateful

799
00:30:55,250 --> 00:30:57,060
and can't tolerate seeing our new classmate

800
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:58,740
being bullied!

801
00:30:58,740 --> 00:30:59,970
I'm kind!

802
00:30:59,970 --> 00:31:01,410
Is Zhu Chao as kind as I am?

803
00:31:01,410 --> 00:31:03,330
Is Xu Wenwu as kind as I am?

804
00:31:03,330 --> 00:31:04,290
-No.
-Absolutely not.

805
00:31:04,290 --> 00:31:05,550
No, neither of them is.

806
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:07,430
You'd better stop talking.

807
00:31:07,450 --> 00:31:09,010
The most despicable one is you.

808
00:31:09,010 --> 00:31:10,780
You changed your sides at the last minute.

809
00:31:10,780 --> 00:31:12,290
You said she was a traitor before;

810
00:31:12,290 --> 00:31:13,410
what does that make you now?

811
00:31:13,410 --> 00:31:14,650
Shut up.

812
00:31:15,650 --> 00:31:16,420
Miaomiao,

813
00:31:16,730 --> 00:31:17,610
I absolutely support you

814
00:31:17,610 --> 00:31:19,050
in my heart.

815
00:31:19,050 --> 00:31:19,820
But look,

816
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:21,570
just the two of us supporting you

817
00:31:21,570 --> 00:31:23,140
isn't enough, right?

818
00:31:23,450 --> 00:31:24,650
Don't be angry, okay?

819
00:31:26,610 --> 00:31:27,290
Okay?

820
00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:28,650
Qiang Xiaowa!

821
00:31:29,130 --> 00:31:30,450
Didn't you promise to vote for me?

822
00:31:30,450 --> 00:31:31,690
Why didn't you do it?

823
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:33,140
I didn't promise.

824
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:35,310
You didn't say no either, did you?

825
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:36,880
Not refusing is the same as agreeing.

826
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,150
How do I usually treat you?

827
00:31:38,150 --> 00:31:39,630
How have I helped you?

828
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:41,420
You can't confuse friends and foes!

829
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:43,340
Right, ever since you came,

830
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:45,000
we've always been good to you.

831
00:31:45,140 --> 00:31:47,130
This behavior is really not right of you.

832
00:31:47,130 --> 00:31:48,010
You're right.

833
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:50,510
Then why did she have only one vote?

834
00:31:51,410 --> 00:31:53,220
Are you trying to sow discord between us?

835
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:54,130
Fine if you didn't vote for her!

836
00:31:54,130 --> 00:31:54,970
I don't care!

837
00:32:11,980 --> 00:32:12,780
Qiang Xiaowa!

838
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,540
What's wrong with you?

839
00:32:15,770 --> 00:32:18,430
Why haven't you worn your school uniform today?

840
00:32:18,450 --> 00:32:20,410
Director Xiao has already told you.

841
00:32:20,410 --> 00:32:21,740
You should put on your uniform

842
00:32:21,740 --> 00:32:23,330
and get your hair cut as soon as possible.

843
00:32:23,330 --> 00:32:25,060
What does it have to do with you?

844
00:32:26,090 --> 00:32:27,550
I'm the Class Monitor now.

845
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:31,170
So what if you're the Class Monitor?

846
00:32:31,170 --> 00:32:32,940
I have the responsibility of leading the whole class.

847
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:33,710
You...

848
00:32:33,780 --> 00:32:35,820
put on your uniform earlier,

849
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:36,860
just like everyone else.

850
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,290
Why should I be like you?

851
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:40,250
I...

852
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:41,730
You...

853
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:44,260
I heard that you didn't even attend PE class

854
00:32:44,260 --> 00:32:45,360
and cried in the classroom

855
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:47,090
because you weren't elected as Class Monitor.

856
00:32:47,090 --> 00:32:47,890
I didn't.

857
00:32:54,250 --> 00:32:55,250
Do you know

858
00:32:55,410 --> 00:32:57,100
why only one person in the whole class

859
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:58,610
voted for you?

860
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:00,890
What?

861
00:33:01,670 --> 00:33:03,090
It means

862
00:33:03,140 --> 00:33:04,260
that only one person in the whole class

863
00:33:04,260 --> 00:33:05,500
thinks you can be the Class Monitor.

864
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,500
It also means

865
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:08,630
that you're not suitable for the role.

866
00:33:11,210 --> 00:33:12,090
So what if

867
00:33:12,090 --> 00:33:14,150
you were to become the Class Monitor?

868
00:33:15,210 --> 00:33:16,610
What's so great about it?

869
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:19,100
Can it give you three heads and six arms?

870
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:19,780
Or

871
00:33:19,780 --> 00:33:22,130
can it help you graduate directly from high school?

872
00:33:22,130 --> 00:33:23,100
Isn't it just

873
00:33:23,100 --> 00:33:24,980
a nicer title to show off?

874
00:33:25,980 --> 00:33:27,510
Is that what you care about?

875
00:33:27,610 --> 00:33:28,730
Of course not.

876
00:33:33,010 --> 00:33:35,470
Don't you love reading martial arts novels?

877
00:33:36,120 --> 00:33:37,580
You know Qiao Feng, right?

878
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:39,350
Did he ever say

879
00:33:39,450 --> 00:33:41,850
he was the leader of the martial arts world?

880
00:33:42,260 --> 00:33:43,100
No.

881
00:33:44,050 --> 00:33:44,810
Did he ever claim

882
00:33:44,810 --> 00:33:47,140
that he was the number one in martial arts?

883
00:33:48,490 --> 00:33:49,450
No.

884
00:33:50,570 --> 00:33:51,970
But he was a great hero,

885
00:33:52,170 --> 00:33:53,230
a true man of honor,

886
00:33:53,450 --> 00:33:54,450
and a good person.

887
00:33:56,110 --> 00:33:57,820
Stop thinking you're talented

888
00:33:57,820 --> 00:33:59,600
just because you're clever in small ways.

889
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:01,060
And don't always think...

890
00:34:05,570 --> 00:34:08,060
-Why are you crying again?
-I’m not.

891
00:34:08,940 --> 00:34:10,690
I just think

892
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:14,389
that Qiao Feng had it so tough.

893
00:34:20,610 --> 00:34:22,850
I just think there are many things

894
00:34:23,130 --> 00:34:24,730
that you can do in your youth.

895
00:34:25,790 --> 00:34:27,050
You should set your sights

896
00:34:27,050 --> 00:34:28,650
on the wider world out there.

897
00:34:29,610 --> 00:34:30,820
Mr. Gao,

898
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:34,010
have you been to Shanghai?

899
00:34:36,889 --> 00:34:38,409
What's it like?

900
00:34:38,850 --> 00:34:40,290
It looks different in everyone's eyes.

901
00:34:40,290 --> 00:34:41,889
Just go and see for yourself.

902
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:45,929
Cheng Miaomiao,

903
00:34:47,139 --> 00:34:48,570
did you help Qiang Xiaowa

904
00:34:49,020 --> 00:34:50,880
just to become the Class Monitor?

905
00:34:51,870 --> 00:34:53,310
Of course not.

906
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:00,330
All right.

907
00:35:01,170 --> 00:35:01,900
Don't cry.

908
00:35:03,890 --> 00:35:04,970
I don't care

909
00:35:04,970 --> 00:35:06,530
whether I'm the Class Monitor or not.

910
00:35:06,530 --> 00:35:07,740
But I still want to

911
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:09,630
continue to help Qiang Xiaowa.

912
00:35:10,060 --> 00:35:12,650
You two... need to help me with this.

913
00:35:13,370 --> 00:35:14,300
Why?

914
00:35:15,250 --> 00:35:17,580
Just tell me whether you'll help me or not.

915
00:35:18,730 --> 00:35:19,410
I will.

916
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:22,180
I will.

917
00:35:31,700 --> 00:35:33,130
Mr. Gao is good.

918
00:35:33,730 --> 00:35:34,700
What did he say to her?

919
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:35,900
Why did she suddenly let it go?

920
00:35:35,900 --> 00:35:36,490
Well,

921
00:35:37,250 --> 00:35:38,260
what does this have to do

922
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:39,790
with helping Qiang Xiaowa?

923
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,530
She said she'd help, so let her.

924
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:42,530
She's hurt right now,

925
00:35:42,530 --> 00:35:43,660
so go along with her.

926
00:35:44,810 --> 00:35:46,970
It's just that it's difficult to help Qiang Xiaowa.

927
00:35:46,970 --> 00:35:48,900
He's just a prickly troublemaker.

928
00:35:49,620 --> 00:35:51,130
A "prickly" troublemaker?

929
00:35:51,130 --> 00:35:52,810
I'll have him get a haircut first.

930
00:35:52,810 --> 00:35:54,410
Prickly troublemaker, huh?

931
00:35:57,890 --> 00:35:59,950
Tell me if you have any difficulties.

932
00:36:00,570 --> 00:36:01,940
I don't have any.

933
00:36:04,610 --> 00:36:06,330
I know we have some grudges,

934
00:36:06,330 --> 00:36:07,710
no, misunderstandings.

935
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:09,100
But they're all in the past.

936
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:09,610
Right?

937
00:36:09,610 --> 00:36:10,780
You left your hometown to come here.

938
00:36:10,780 --> 00:36:12,090
My home is right here.

939
00:36:12,410 --> 00:36:13,970
Yes, you live here.

940
00:36:14,410 --> 00:36:16,170
But don't you have to cross the bridge to get here?

941
00:36:16,170 --> 00:36:17,810
Since you're here, you're a guest.

942
00:36:17,810 --> 00:36:19,290
And since Cheng Miaomiao considers you a friend,

943
00:36:19,290 --> 00:36:20,370
I will too.

944
00:36:20,770 --> 00:36:21,340
From now on,

945
00:36:21,340 --> 00:36:22,780
if you need anything, just let me know.

946
00:36:22,780 --> 00:36:23,380
At the whole No. 2 High School...

947
00:36:23,380 --> 00:36:24,810
No, at the entire Linqi Base,

948
00:36:24,810 --> 00:36:26,070
my words carry weight.

949
00:36:26,310 --> 00:36:27,390
Didn't you say

950
00:36:27,490 --> 00:36:30,420
that none of the families on your side are doing well?

951
00:36:31,850 --> 00:36:33,060
I didn't mean that.

952
00:36:33,120 --> 00:36:34,140
I mean,

953
00:36:34,450 --> 00:36:35,090
I know an uncle

954
00:36:35,090 --> 00:36:37,020
who is really good at cutting hair,

955
00:36:37,370 --> 00:36:38,630
and he does it for free.

956
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:43,660
See? I told you. I should be the one to do it.

957
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:45,660
I could move him through emotions and reason with him logically.

958
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:46,700
At least I could make some progress.

959
00:36:46,700 --> 00:36:49,160
It's better than sending that big fool over.

960
00:36:49,180 --> 00:36:51,580
He came to him and said that his family was poor. That's it.

961
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:52,820
We've messed up again.

962
00:36:52,820 --> 00:36:54,750
You really can't blame me for this.

963
00:36:54,850 --> 00:36:55,490
I went

964
00:36:55,490 --> 00:36:57,530
with the genuine intention of helping him,

965
00:36:57,530 --> 00:36:58,530
but he's just too sensitive

966
00:36:58,530 --> 00:36:59,780
and thought I was insulting his family.

967
00:36:59,780 --> 00:37:01,490
I didn't mean it that way at all.

968
00:37:01,490 --> 00:37:01,930
Don't you know

969
00:37:01,930 --> 00:37:03,260
what kind of person I am?

970
00:37:03,890 --> 00:37:05,090
Let's not talk about our class;

971
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:06,570
let's talk about the entire grade.

972
00:37:06,570 --> 00:37:08,190
Who hasn't eaten the snacks I bought?

973
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:09,620
Who hasn't drunk the beverages I bought?

974
00:37:09,620 --> 00:37:10,970
Whose birthday have I not given a gift to?

975
00:37:10,970 --> 00:37:12,490
But on my birthday, who gave me a gift?

976
00:37:12,490 --> 00:37:13,830
Have I ever looked down on anyone?

977
00:37:13,830 --> 00:37:15,560
How can you look down on anyone?

978
00:37:15,740 --> 00:37:16,850
You sound like you're doing charity

979
00:37:16,850 --> 00:37:17,890
by playing with them.

980
00:37:17,890 --> 00:37:18,730
Your family

981
00:37:18,730 --> 00:37:19,810
earns a lot

982
00:37:19,810 --> 00:37:21,330
because your mom runs a restaurant.

983
00:37:21,330 --> 00:37:22,290
What does that have to do with you?

984
00:37:22,290 --> 00:37:22,970
When have I or Hu ever

985
00:37:22,970 --> 00:37:25,300
missed giving you a gift on your birthday?

986
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,560
The transformers, game cartridges

987
00:37:27,580 --> 00:37:29,410
my brother bought,

988
00:37:29,410 --> 00:37:30,450
and even his belt—

989
00:37:30,450 --> 00:37:31,650
I gave them all to you.

990
00:37:32,170 --> 00:37:34,020
Vivian Chow, Charlie Yeung,

991
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:35,810
Faye Wong, A-Mei,

992
00:37:35,850 --> 00:37:37,680
Sammi Cheng, and Gigi Leung—

993
00:37:38,130 --> 00:37:39,810
which album by them have I not bought for you?

994
00:37:39,810 --> 00:37:41,580
9.8 yuan per album, all official versions.

995
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:42,660
Over the years, my monthly allowance

996
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:43,730
went from five yuan to twenty,

997
00:37:43,730 --> 00:37:45,610
and every penny you spent chasing your celebrity crushes

998
00:37:45,610 --> 00:37:47,130
came from my pocket.

999
00:37:50,120 --> 00:37:50,920
Yes. Yes.

1000
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:53,210
That's why,

1001
00:37:53,210 --> 00:37:54,580
apart from my mom and grandma,

1002
00:37:54,580 --> 00:37:56,170
you two are the closest people to me in the whole world.

1003
00:37:56,170 --> 00:37:58,140
That's why the three of us are an inseparable trio.

1004
00:37:58,140 --> 00:37:58,820
If anything happens

1005
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:00,090
to you in the future...

1006
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:02,290
No, no matter what happens to you,

1007
00:38:02,290 --> 00:38:03,820
I'll be the first to step up.

1008
00:38:04,970 --> 00:38:07,170
Then go help Qiang Xiaowa until the end.

1009
00:38:08,240 --> 00:38:10,160
I just don't get along with him.

1010
00:38:10,370 --> 00:38:12,090
We'd better stay away from each other.

1011
00:38:12,090 --> 00:38:13,730
I can't let Mr. Gao think

1012
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:15,050
that my words don't count

1013
00:38:15,050 --> 00:38:15,780
just because I didn't

1014
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:16,970
become the Class Monitor.

1015
00:38:16,970 --> 00:38:18,650
I have to prove to him

1016
00:38:18,650 --> 00:38:19,480
that I didn't do this

1017
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:21,130
to become the Class Monitor.

1018
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:22,540
Do you know Qiao Feng?

1019
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:24,140
He was always generous to everyone.

1020
00:38:24,140 --> 00:38:25,470
That's a hero's spirit.

1021
00:38:25,700 --> 00:38:26,300
Wait,

1022
00:38:26,640 --> 00:38:28,840
what does this have to do with Qiao Feng?

1023
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:31,930
You wouldn't understand, even if I explained.

1024
00:38:31,930 --> 00:38:33,770
But even if Qiao Feng were here,

1025
00:38:33,770 --> 00:38:34,940
it wouldn't help.

1026
00:38:35,210 --> 00:38:37,290
Qiang Xiaowa is just so stubborn.

1027
00:38:37,570 --> 00:38:40,410
We're just trying to be friends with him, right?

1028
00:38:40,820 --> 00:38:42,100
There's no bad blood.

1029
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:43,550
It's not like we have a crush on him

1030
00:38:43,550 --> 00:38:45,290
or want to date him to be his girlfriend,

1031
00:38:45,290 --> 00:38:46,820
so why does he act like that?

1032
00:38:47,610 --> 00:38:49,620
Exactly. He's so full of himself.

1033
00:38:50,810 --> 00:38:52,740
We're all just trying to be nice...

1034
00:38:53,580 --> 00:38:55,910
but he acts like someone has a crush on him.

1035
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:57,070
If he keeps this up,

1036
00:38:57,090 --> 00:38:58,330
I bet Fang will return him

1037
00:38:58,330 --> 00:38:59,610
to his old school sooner or later.

1038
00:38:59,610 --> 00:39:01,900
Miaomiao, don't blame yourself for that.

1039
00:39:01,900 --> 00:39:03,340
Why should I?

1040
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:06,440
It's not like it's my fault if he gets returned.

1041
00:39:13,950 --> 00:39:15,690
Yaya, follow me later.

1042
00:39:15,710 --> 00:39:18,010
I'll teach you the essentials of being a referee.

1043
00:39:18,010 --> 00:39:19,010
-Okay.
-Pengfei.

1044
00:39:19,140 --> 00:39:19,600
Come on.

1045
00:39:22,450 --> 00:39:23,760
-Come on!
-Daiyu.

1046
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:24,650
Chen!

1047
00:39:24,650 --> 00:39:25,980
Okay, thank you, Daiyu.

1048
00:39:27,530 --> 00:39:28,340
Mom,

1049
00:39:28,390 --> 00:39:29,410
can I have a bottle of this,

1050
00:39:29,410 --> 00:39:30,180
please?

1051
00:39:30,290 --> 00:39:31,220
These are for adults.

1052
00:39:31,220 --> 00:39:32,500
They have artificial coloring.

1053
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:33,340
I've never heard that artificial coloring

1054
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:35,020
is only harmful to kids.

1055
00:39:35,730 --> 00:39:36,810
You drink this.

1056
00:39:37,180 --> 00:39:37,980
Put that back.

1057
00:39:38,140 --> 00:39:39,010
I'm too old

1058
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:40,360
to still drink this.

1059
00:39:42,060 --> 00:39:43,680
What's Cheng Yaya doing over there?

1060
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:46,140
Your dad's explaining referee stuff to him.

1061
00:39:46,290 --> 00:39:47,290
Why didn't he explain it to me?

1062
00:39:47,290 --> 00:39:48,900
I want to be a referee too.

1063
00:39:49,130 --> 00:39:50,790
Do you think you'd understand?

1064
00:39:50,790 --> 00:39:51,520
Li Si is here.

1065
00:39:52,020 --> 00:39:52,570
Auntie.

1066
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,060
Where are your parents?

1067
00:39:54,060 --> 00:39:56,050
My mom... My mom's at the restaurant.

1068
00:39:56,050 --> 00:39:56,890
My dad...

1069
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:58,400
Isn't he over there?

1070
00:39:58,400 --> 00:39:59,200
Do you want it?

1071
00:40:00,140 --> 00:40:00,810
Good.

1072
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:03,200
We should organize more of these events.

1073
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:04,370
Your staff hospital

1074
00:40:04,370 --> 00:40:06,570
really excels in this kind of activity.

1075
00:40:06,610 --> 00:40:07,120
Yes.

1076
00:40:07,430 --> 00:40:08,630
Your frontline

1077
00:40:08,660 --> 00:40:10,210
mainly has too many tasks, right?

1078
00:40:10,210 --> 00:40:11,340
The work is intense,

1079
00:40:11,410 --> 00:40:12,290
and time is always tight.

1080
00:40:12,290 --> 00:40:13,130
It's not easy for you

1081
00:40:13,130 --> 00:40:14,330
to organize an event.

1082
00:40:14,640 --> 00:40:16,480
The frontline work is tough.

1083
00:40:17,130 --> 00:40:18,250
Look at the weather.

1084
00:40:18,250 --> 00:40:20,220
And we're already wearing long sleeves in the mountains.

1085
00:40:20,220 --> 00:40:21,570
It’s cold in the middle of the night, freezing.

1086
00:40:21,570 --> 00:40:23,540
Really? You have to take care of yourself.

1087
00:40:23,540 --> 00:40:24,180
Dr. Cheng,

1088
00:40:24,890 --> 00:40:25,570
we'll start

1089
00:40:25,570 --> 00:40:26,340
in ten minutes.

1090
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,180
Okay. Okay.

1091
00:40:27,850 --> 00:40:29,050
It's... It's about to start.

1092
00:40:29,050 --> 00:40:29,890
There's still time.

1093
00:40:29,890 --> 00:40:31,350
Why don't you warm up a bit?

1094
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,490
I don't know how.

1095
00:40:35,150 --> 00:40:36,110
Fine, fine.

1096
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:43,180
Pick up the thumbtack there, or it could hurt your feet.

1097
00:40:43,180 --> 00:40:44,710
Where is there a thumbtack?

1098
00:40:49,530 --> 00:40:50,220
Nice!

1099
00:40:59,130 --> 00:40:59,810
Let me.

1100
00:41:00,470 --> 00:41:01,180
Catch it. Catch it.

1101
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:02,800
[Red Team 6]

1102
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:02,800
[Blue Team 9]

1103
00:41:06,660 --> 00:41:07,300
Nice play!

1104
00:41:10,890 --> 00:41:11,530
Nice play!

1105
00:41:13,580 --> 00:41:14,250
Good!

1106
00:41:26,910 --> 00:41:27,580
Catch it!

1107
00:41:31,540 --> 00:41:32,470
Nice shot!

1108
00:41:43,130 --> 00:41:43,930
Over there.

1109
00:41:45,220 --> 00:41:45,900
Miaomiao.

1110
00:41:46,180 --> 00:41:48,230
Something has happened to Hu Qiumin.

1111
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:48,870
Let's go.

1112
00:41:51,210 --> 00:41:51,960
Nice!

1113
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:25,650
Li Si, Hu Qiumin, and I

1114
00:42:26,170 --> 00:42:27,100
first met

1115
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:28,490
when we were three years old.

1116
00:42:28,490 --> 00:42:29,260
Hu always says

1117
00:42:29,260 --> 00:42:29,930
we've been together even earlier,

1118
00:42:29,930 --> 00:42:30,930
since we were two.

1119
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:32,030
The elderly say

1120
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:34,390
that kids can't form memories before the age of three.

1121
00:42:34,390 --> 00:42:34,760
So,

1122
00:42:34,790 --> 00:42:36,010
from age three onward, our memories,

1123
00:42:36,010 --> 00:42:38,530
apart from family, are of each other.

1124
00:42:38,970 --> 00:42:40,010
All the little things,

1125
00:42:40,010 --> 00:42:41,290
and running all over the place.

1126
00:42:41,290 --> 00:42:42,490
We've fought,

1127
00:42:42,490 --> 00:42:43,130
argued,

1128
00:42:43,330 --> 00:42:45,620
and threatened to end our friendship countless times.

1129
00:42:45,620 --> 00:42:48,100
But none of us ever really left the others.

1130
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:49,780
Once, our Chinese teacher

1131
00:42:49,780 --> 00:42:52,010
assigned us to write a composition about friendship.

1132
00:42:52,010 --> 00:42:52,800
I wrote,

1133
00:42:53,250 --> 00:42:54,180
"steaming hot."

1134
00:42:54,730 --> 00:42:55,500
The teacher said

1135
00:42:55,500 --> 00:42:56,850
that's how you describe food,

1136
00:42:56,850 --> 00:42:58,180
like a bowl of hot rice.

1137
00:42:58,570 --> 00:42:59,330
Yeah.

1138
00:42:59,330 --> 00:43:00,970
Our friendship is like rice,

1139
00:43:01,180 --> 00:43:02,180
steaming hot.
